@startuml
'https://plantuml.com/sequence-diagram

autonumber

title Update Airport Details: Simplified Sequence Diagram

actor "Backoffice Operator" as BO
participant ":System" as S

BO -> S: Asks to update an Airport's details
S --> BO: Requests Iata Code and New Details

BO -> S: Types requested data
S --> BO: Updates the airport details

@enduml